# bundle_membership.algo.ct
# Bounded algorithm framing for ProbeBundle membership, split witnesses,
# cancellation, and result inversion over decoded bundle streams.
#
# Program:
#   Production i emits 1 followed by the 7-bit binary index i.
#   Run for exactly the input length. The remaining tape is the concatenation
#   of the production for each input position whose bit was 1.
#
# Scope:
#   This is a real cyclic-tag positional certificate for streams of length at
#   most 128. The C harness checks the decoded Bundle semantics and verifies
#   this CT certificate for each Bundle fixture.
